text: Polli Sree College () is an intermediate college in Bangladesh. It is located in the village of Madertala in Dumuria Upazila under Khulna District. It was established in 1994. It originated from a Polli Sree School. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Colleges in Khulna District Category:Khulna District
